stories.title: Styris leads New Zealand to thrilling win
stories.subTitle: New Zealand v Pakistan, 1st ODI, Auckland
stories.summary: Scott Styris scored a magnificent 101 not out as New Zealand squeaked through to a four-wicket win against Pakistan at Auckland to go 1-0 up in the five-match series
